social_posts.post_text: No matter how big or how small, knowing I reached even ONE person and touched their heart, makes it all so worth it. Thank you. I am so honored I get to get to connect with so many of you through sound. Such a gift. Together makes everything better 🌍🎶🙏🏽🤍

Closing out the year strong in Los Angeles, San Francisco, Colombia, Mexico, and London for NYE at @thesteelyardldn ⚡️ it’s going to be such a wicked month. Also, early 2023 confirmed for Israel and 2 weekends in India! First stop, Tel Aviv, see you January 20th for @midburnil @shliff_camp fundraiser event! And finally heading to India with @slickingitup ~ I’m so excited! Let’s go! 🫠🎶🔥

Excited for a stacked weekend! First stop, Los Angeles this Friday for a very special night with @adanatwins @fideles_music @deerjade_ @aether.music and @oostil__ x @set.underground ~ going to be MAD! San Francisco, you’re up next! See you soon! 🎶🫶🏽🪐🤤 (ticket links in bio) || some memories from earlier this year in LA ⚡️

Crazy that even after having made the decision to slow down from touring until the end of the year, I’m still playing in 4 different continents in the coming weeks . I can’t help myself but say yes, when these bookings come in 🥹🫠 I love what I do. Touring is about to go back into full swing next year! I can’t wait and am so turned ON for 2023! Comment your flags & show me where you want to see me in 2023 🎶🤸🏽‍♀️🔥 ~ for now, I’ll see you tonight, Los Angeles. San Francisco, you’re up next tomorrow! 2023 starts off with me performing in a few NEW continents, to be announced. 🇬🇧🇮🇱🇮🇳 ~ who’s coming?! Let me see your flags! 👏🏽👏🏽

This weekend was bonkers! I had sooo much fun with @setunderground ~ both events were absolutely wild! I had such a blast with you guys. Thank you Los Angeles for always showing up so strongly for me. It’s always so special to play in my home-town. San Francisco you were just beautiful! Both nights were truly unforgettable. The energy, the crowd, the production and all the other talented artists…10/10 all around! Thank you so much. 🥲🎶💗|| Next up, Colombia and Mexico this weekend! Ticket links in bio. See you soon! 🇨🇴🎶🇲🇽

2023 is near… and I couldn’t feel more ready to bring in the new year. I’m preparing a ton of new music, tour dates, merch dropz and a lot of outstanding new releases on my imprint @earprnmusic || SO many amazing projects underway! It’s going to be an AMAZING year together, you guys! I can feel it.

Guadalajara, you were INSANE! Your energy was just 🔥 ~ @dmtclubgdl is one of the most unique, trippy and intentional venues I’ve been to, to date. You have to visit to understand. Thank you, Mexico! 🌎🙏🏽🐸❤️ || Shout out to @alexdondmt @tensystems_ofc @zieze.ofc @guillermocosio @henry.viixii @jihaddipp

Immaculate vibes last weekend in Colombia and Mexico. Still buzzing! I am now getting ready for the last show of the year with the legendary Fox&Badge community at the iconic venue @thesteelyardldn ~ beyond excited to welcome in 2023 with you all, in this way! London, get ready! 🇬🇧🎶🤘🏽

➝  photos by @chivography x @dmtclubgdl

LONDON! Overwhelmed with excitement for tonight’s show at @thesteelyardldn 🇬🇧 || FOX&BADGE for New Years Eve 2022. Set time is midnight to 3:00am. What a beautiful way to start the new year together. It’s going to be pure MAGIC. With that said, I just want to thank you all for an incredible year. So grateful for all the beautiful opportunities, adventures and memories we all share. I love you guys. READY for 2023, baby! Let’s get it! 🔥🎶🤘🏽❤️

Woah! What a CRAZY New Year’s event with FOX&BADGE at  @thesteelyardldn in London 🇬🇧🎉🎶🌈 ~ ohhhh my! 😮 || it was a true honor to bring in the first moments of 2023 (last slide is the MIDNIGHT moment) and what a truly special experience it was to collaborate with other performers and performances simultaneously, together bringing a true story of CONNECTION, TOUCH, INTIMACY, LOVE & KINK. An essence of what I myself, my project, my music, and my label Ear Porn Music are all about @earprnmusic — super powerful and memorable in all forms. So with that, BIG thank you to everyone who joined me during my debut in London and special thanks to FOX&BADGE for inviting me and allowing me the honor to bring in 2023! 🥂

In the mean time…Tel Aviv! You’re next. See you next week for the for the @midburnil @shliff_camp Fundraiser Event 28.01.22 ✈️🎶🔥❤️

The videos don’t do it justice. They just don’t. That party was nuts! TEL AVIV! You freakin’ rock. Shout out to @cornfest for her first ever video duties 😂 ~ we captured just a few very short snippets of what was truly an extraordinary night together. Hats off to @midburnil @shliff_camp 🍄 for putting on an amazing event and for bringing me out from across the world to contribute to it. The entire camp is full of beautiful, kind, creative individuals. I think it’s safe to say, that was one for the books. I had the best time. Hope to make it to the official Mid Burn this year. touuuuur has been amazing 🎶 but I haven’t had a sunday like this in a long time! ☺️ morning walk, cold breeze,  pups, mantras…all smiles! happy sunday!

4 continents, 6 weeks. Los Angeles, San Francisco, Colombia, Mexico, London, Tel Aviv….🔥 ~ what a time that was! Thank you to everyone who came out to dance the night away with me…so many unforgettable moments! AND a massive THANK YOU to all who continuously support me…my fans, my colleagues, my team, the event organizers, promoters, my family and friends! all of you! You are all just the best and I feel extremely blessed. I LOVE this life with you all. 🎶🤍

I’m working on something special, the largest music project of my career as an artist. I missed this so much…being back in my creative space, doing what I love most ~ a little something special I started recording late last night 🎶🤍 #novation #analog #synthesizer
Austin! See you tomorrow at @theconcourseproject alongside @furcoatmusic @mayajanecolesofficial & @gordoszn ~ gonna be a fun night! 🎶❤️

Hey everyone! So, I wanted to share that last month my team and I decided to postpone all of my tour dates in March so that I could stay in my studio to finish up a very big and important project. I am working on a large body of work that is the most special and important project I have ever worked on to date. I have evolved immensely both as an artist, but also just as a soul, as a woman, and feel it’s time to really share that journey and story with you all. As my touring schedules have gradually become very heavy since Tomorrowland Belgium 2022 all way through the Fall, Winter and beginning of this year, we feel it is time to take a little time off so that I can focus on the music I am making and beyond ready and excited to share with you guys. It’s an extremely exciting and inspiring time for me as a musician and as a producer ~ so it feels in alignment that I take the energy away from traveling, performances, time zone shifts and preserve it for all that’s been flowing in my creative space. I know I have been sharing a lot of sneak peaks recently on my story and on my feed, and you can expect to see a lot more of that too over the next few months. The project that is to come is the symbol of my entering a new phase and chapter as a producer and a performer. It is going to be a really fun and exciting journey with all of you, my fans and our global community! I plan to return back to a light touring schedule in April, followed by an exciting tour Europe to come end of April and early May. I am so sorry to all my fans in India who were expecting to see me after the announcements I had around my tour this coming month ~ we postponed the tour to Fall 2023 are excited for a two weekend tour in 4 major cities in India! Will be worth the wait. I promise. Soon, many of you will understand why I made this decision and we’ll come back together again, stronger than ever. For now, I’ll see you guys at the end of next month. Europe you’ll be first to catch a taste of what’s coming 🥹🎶🤍

See you all soon! 

With love, 

Lauren Mia x
“The Beginning” ~~ it’s coming… 🎶🙏🏽🌎
week seven complete of my studio hibernation ~ wait until you hear what’s coming! it’s BIG 🎶♾️🎹

lately! 🎶🔥 —-> swipe all the way to see a tiny glimpse of the moment I composed what I feel is the most beautiful melody I’ve written to date 💗 don’t want to spoil anything too much, too soon, but it’s coming you guys! I’m so ready to share with you all & connect with you all again in this way! We’re almost there 🙌🏽 #rebirth

✈️ finally back home after a pretty intense travel day yesterday, (one of those) 🙈 ~ buuuut we made it! straight back to studio to finish up another new project >> then, all the fun planning comes! mmmhm…I can’t wait. Happy Monday, friendzz! 👽🎶💛🎹💋😋

𓂀• 𝐑𝐄:𝐁𝐈𝐑𝐓𝐇 • 𓂀 

Thousands and thousands of hours went into this project…no exaggeration whatsoever. The joy I feel inside my being is indescribable, especially with these last 3 months of being in full-time studio mode…just feeling like my decisions and sacrifice are really paying off. I know this will all continue to unfold in time. 
Countless hours, sleepless nights, smiles, tears, laughter, excitement, joy…breaking new barriers, new limits, and reaching new levels of skill and sound…new goals. Bringing my sonic visions, dreams, and essence of being, heart and soul through a sonic experience to be shared with you all. To me, at the end of it all, this is why I do what I do. To create. To invent. Here’s a few videos from the last week recording and wrapping up the final piece of this body of work. I’m so incredibly excited! Are you ready? It’s time! 𓆃

Friends! I’m only playing one show this month after finishing RE:BIRTH and my insane, yet EPIC studio hibernation. So this is a special night, indeed. I’ll be headlining a fun event in San Diego showcasing a brand new sound-system as well as a TON of new IDs from RE:BIRTH𓂀 ~ You’ll be the first to hear! See you back on the dance-floor soon again. For now, enjoy the very first tiny glimpse of one of my unreleased singles ‘Ashes in Paradise’ 🎶🔥

I felt a black&white image made sense to announce my first single 𝑺𝑯𝑨𝑫𝑶𝑾 coming out next month. This piece was about the shadow-work I invested and devoted myself to doing throughout the last 2 and a half years, to grow and evolve as a soul, as a young woman, and as an artist during my cosmic right of passage into adulthood — my Saturn Return. So it’s been a long time coming, but I see now, all in divine timing. I can’t wait to share this piece with you, the first of many to come in the next few months. I’m so excited, happy, and so ready. In honor of it all, I wanted to share the art for the very first time, as well as some raw moments of me producing the record and working through the vocal arrangement and overall production of this track. A little glimpse into my world during my creative process. 🎶 

‘Shadow’ (Original Mix) out this September!

1 week in the jungle ~ shooting the visual element and story of RE:BIRTH. It was not an easy journey and re-tested my limits and strengths all over again, but it was all so worth it. So proud of our team for working tirelessly everyday from dawn until night to get this done to fulfill my vision, in blistering heat, while all slowly devoured by copious amounts of mosquitoes 🙈 ~ thank you all…and thanks to me, for having the strength and courage to tell my story, writing it, producing it, and even styling myself (no glam team for this, and the only woman on site, just mgmt and video crew) SO, I can say I am proud in many ways and for many reasons, and might I just say, WE crushed it. I cannot wait to share this piece with you all. I’ve already wrapped up the audio for this story, and now all I have to do is record myself tonight, sharing with you this story for you all to understand and to connect with me on a deeper level. It’s exciting because for the first time, it’ll be told not just through my sounds and melodies, but through my voice ✨🫶🏽 11.14

My FIRST single of my FIRST Album is out in 2 weeks. I still cannot even believe it. The amount of energy, focus, dedication, hard-work, and sacrifice it has taken me to get here throughout the last 7 years of my musical journey is indescribable. In some ways, it’s actually extremely painful to think about, yet incredibly rewarding at the same time. 2022 and 2023 was the year I made big and tough decisions, took major risks, stood up for myself, stood my ground, and said “I’m going to follow my heart and do things my way, the way that feels right to me.” It’s safe to say that the advice my father always gave me growing up was 100% right…he said, “risks have their rewards” ~ so here it is. I’m officially announcing the release of my very first single which will be out this September 28th ~  𝑺𝑯𝑨𝑫𝑶𝑾 — this single is the first of three leading up to the release of my very first large body of work which I am so deeply proud of, my first album ~ 𓂀• 𝐑𝐄:𝐁𝐈𝐑𝐓𝐇 • 𓂀 || the album is due to release on November 14th, 2023 ~ my 30th trip around the sun. There is no better way I would have imagined to enter this new decade and era for me as a human, soul, woman, and artist. I’m so excited for what’s ahead of us all, together. I put my entire soul, essence and ALL of my heart and energy into this album. Now, the time has come to finally begin to share it. Thank you from the bottom of my heart to my family, friends, musical soul mates, colleagues, my small yet incredible & valuable team behind me (you know who you are), and lastly my incredibly fans around the globe. The first single is the first record I am putting out in over 1 year and a half. It’s a big deal to me. I’m nervous, excited, but so ready. Thank you for receiving me and thank you so much for supporting me. And to the ones who doubted me, let me show you what I got. I love you all so much, and I am so ready to gift you 13 beautiful tracks from my heart to yours. 🎶🌎🙏🏽❤️ 

‘Shadow’ (Original Mix) out 28.09.23

Scroll down to know more about ‘Shadow’ and what this song is all about. 

“Multi-disciplinary musician and producer Lauren Mia has officially announced her debut album RE:BIRTH. The intricate musical web she weaves across her unique, analog soundscapes of Melodic Techno and Progressive House has shaped an ethereal, dynamic signature sound brimming with sacred texture and identity that has set the stage for her debut album. RE:BIRTH’s lead single “Shadow” was written about Lauren’s own personal shadow-work, a process of deep reflection and commitment to self-awareness to get to know the parts of oneself that often subconsciously lurk in the shadows of our minds. Sonically, the album’s first single is an expansive arrangement juxtaposed between a dynamic percussive profile and innovative synthesis, next-generation melodic techno. With entrancing vocals masterfully sewn into the captivating analog sounds and soul of the track, “Shadow” is a brooding introduction and strong first single that lays the groundwork for the poignant body of work that is Lauren Mia’s RE:BIRTH.”

𝐑𝐄:𝐁𝐈𝐑𝐓𝐇 is near 𓆃
I am so over-the-moon that the first single from my album RE:BIRTH released. From @spotify ‘Electronic Rising’ & ‘Tunnel Vision’ playlist support, to the captivating article from @wonderland and all of all of YOUR support…I am feeling humbled, grateful, and extremely excited. Great news! Every few weeks, starting from yesterday’s release, you get a NEW one from me, leading all the way up until the release of the whole album (14.11.23) — get ready! Next up, c͟e͟r͟e͟m͟o͟n͟y͟𓆗

There are no words to fully describe the heartbreak and pain I feel within my heart and body. The tragedies that are taking place in our world today…they are unfathomable. I just want to share where I am at and how I feel in a fully transparent way. Yesterday, I had a new song of mine come out, CEREMONY. The second song I have put out in over 1 year, and the second single from debut album RE:BIRTH, which I have worked soooo hard for in every aspect one can imagine, to create and bring to life and put out on my own. I’ve been waiting for this moment for so long, and I could not bring my self to post about it, celebrate it our treat it as any normal release-day. All I feel is pure devastation. Nothing can compare or steal my focus and my eyes are swollen from the amount of tears I have shed in the last several days. 

I don’t think many people understand what is happening right now. Not fully. But as sorry and sad as I am to admit this, soon everyone will. Outside of that, things feel separate, far, irrelevant, and life just “has to go on”. Right. Well, not for me. Feels like my life has taken  pause. I am heartbroken, and I am scared. We all have to act NOW to heal humanity and literally fix our world. We’re starting to hit a breaking point as a collective. The last few years were just the start. I am trying to find my hope right now, trying to believe things will be okay soon. But when I look around, what I see…we are a long way from things being okay. We have a serious issue to deal with. A serious threat against our world peace & humanity as a whole. (continued in comments below….) ↴

Grateful and humbled to announce that the SECOND lead single from my debut album RE:BIRTH came out last Thursday ~ 𓂀

I couldn’t bring myself to share or post about it, but I’ve come to realize the world needs art and music more than ever now. This song was made with so much intention and love. I created this piece to illustrate the journey of healing, self love, through sound, and incorporate sacred ancient instruments and elements such as Tibetan Sound Bowls, The Shell Horn, Water, and underlying mantras, all of which has a massive impact on me as an individual. Plant Medicines, meditation and spirituality as a whole has been a pivotal part of my evolution as as soul, as a woman, and as an artist. This song is an ode to that, and my intention is to share and recreate the journey and essence of what Ceremony is like…not an easy or pleasant journey, but life changing in the most positive ways one could imagine. The world needs healing more than ever. Perhaps this will inspire us all to find news way to honor ourselves and those around us.

Ashes in Paradise ~ a song which melodies I composed in pure flow state, all within one day and one night. This is a compilation of the day and night this song came to me. It’s rare I manage to capture myself when in flow-state, but I feel SO grateful that I did. My significant other heard me jumping around and screaming in the other room too, and came in to listen. So some more clips were captured ( these without my knowing) which feels quite vulnerable for me to share. Lol and my hand movements 🙈
but it’s real and raw. I was like in  a little kid this day; and it was exciting to share after discovering I had something really special. These are those moments compiled in a short clip. I hope you enjoy it :)
